rows.label: qst201613_msg0002
rows.name: Nanakoori, everything okay?

rows.label: qst201613_msg0003
rows.name:
...can't...
I... I can't...

rows.label: qst201613_msg0004
rows.name:
I cannot fault her for getting
nervous when faced with a task
of these proportions...

rows.label: qst201613_msg0005
rows.name:
Just remember to breathe, okay?
Try not to tense up.

rows.label: qst201613_msg0006
rows.name:
It's...no use, I'm scared stiff...
Can't move, can barely speak...

rows.label: qst201613_msg0007
rows.name: Those are some serious symptoms...

rows.label: qst201613_msg0008
rows.name: What we do? What we do?!

rows.label: qst201613_msg0009
rows.name:
Maybe we buy something again?
Friend Nanakoori, want eat something?!

rows.label: qst201613_msg0010
rows.name:
...No, I don't need anything...
I don't think I could even...
swallow...anything...

rows.label: qst201613_msg0011
rows.name:
Nanakoori...
You've got loads of fans waiting
for you out there. What's wrong?

rows.label: qst201613_msg0012
rows.name: I... I know that, believe me...

rows.label: qst201613_msg0013
rows.name:
And I would like to...end all of this
on a high, successful note...

rows.label: qst201613_msg0014
rows.name:
But...I can't shake this dread,
I can't stop thinking these thoughts,
and I... I can't sing...

rows.label: qst201613_msg0015
rows.name:
Mmmeehhh, Pi is
fresh out of ideas!

rows.label: qst201613_msg0016
rows.name:
What do we do?
I don't want to force Nanakoori to
do anything against her will...

rows.label: qst201613_msg0017
rows.name:
Is it the singing that she's
stressed about?

rows.label: qst201613_msg0018
rows.name:
Tora think issue is weight of
expectations from big-big audience,
and resulting pressure on self.

rows.label: qst201613_msg0019
rows.name:
But think about it...
When Nanakoori sang for the first time,
she seemed to really be enjoying it.

rows.label: qst201613_msg0020
rows.name: She does love to sing, I'm sure of it.

rows.label: qst201613_msg0021
rows.name:
Now that friend say, it true.
Pi remember the beautiful singing
and the beautiful happy expression.

rows.label: qst201613_msg0022
rows.name:
Hey, how about we ask that girl
from Torigo to come here?

rows.label: qst201613_msg0023
rows.name:
Ohh, I get it!
Remind Nanakoori of how it all started!

rows.label: qst201613_msg0024
rows.name:
Right!
That might unblock something inside
her and make her want to sing again.

rows.label: qst201613_msg0025
rows.name:
It seem worth a try, meh.
Can Pi count on friends?

rows.label: qst201613_msg0026
rows.name: Of course!

rows.label: qst201613_msg0027
rows.name:
We met her at night, at
Tretl Windmill Plaza, right?

rows.label: qst201613_msg0028
rows.name: Yeah, that's it.

rows.label: qst201613_msg0029
rows.name: Okay, friends. Hurry-hurry then!
